name: Market Crash
description: One day it is "To the Moon" and then all of a sudden, it is nothing but pain. The basic laws of Physics apply to financial markets, mainly, What goes up, must come down. And when it goes down, boy does it go down! Major Pain for your portfolio. I created this to celebrate the Crypto Blood Bath of 2021. It was rough, but remember this rule: Buy the Dips!!
